pull.title: ci, gha: Add "x86_64: Linux (Debian stable)" GitHub Actions job
pull.body:
Move more non-x86_64 tasks from Cirrus CI to GitHub Actions.

Solves one item in https://github.com/bitcoin-core/secp256k1/issues/1392 partially.

Based on https://github.com/bitcoin-core/secp256k1/pull/1396.

Includes clean up from https://github.com/bitcoin-core/secp256k1/pull/1405.

repo.name: secp256k1
repo.description: Optimized C library for EC operations on curve secp256k1
